    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>点击点击点击！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clicker Clicker Clicker 是一款点击游戏，在游戏过程中您需要进行一大波的点击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/353e06373ff112a1fbd0df9747894404.poster.avif?t=1754489279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/353e06373ff112a1fbd0df9747894404.webm?t=1754489279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/353e06373ff112a1fbd0df9747894404.mp4?t=1754489279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你点击主光标时，金色的下落光标就会开始生成。它们的生成速度取决于你的点击进度。点击这些掉落光标会获得比主动点击更多的点击金币奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/7c9b81ed772aedecb3c744cdfd4a0a2b.poster.avif?t=1754489279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/7c9b81ed772aedecb3c744cdfd4a0a2b.webm?t=1754489279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/7c9b81ed772aedecb3c744cdfd4a0a2b.mp4?t=1754489279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>点击飞升!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飞升并重新开始游戏可获得点击飞升币，这种币可用于购买永久升级。这些点击飞升没有上限，这意味着只要你愿意，就可以一直玩下去，不断进阶！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/fe921bfdf8e915f3ee1a299a9dd461ce.poster.avif?t=1754489279\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/fe921bfdf8e915f3ee1a299a9dd461ce.webm?t=1754489279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187730/extras/fe921bfdf8e915f3ee1a299a9dd461ce.mp4?t=1754489279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
